WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.500
A drone slowly approaches Gwangan Bridge.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:11.500
Beyond the blue water, Gwangalli Beach and Busan's skyline come into view.

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:17.500
White suspension towers and cables cross the center of the frame.

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:23.500
Cars move across the bridge while the sea glimmers below.

00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:30.266
The camera follows Gwangan Bridge across the Busan coastline.
